On March 18 , 2018 , Al Hajj officially announced the cost of the hashtag , which started on March 18 , 2018 , as well as a total of $ 405 million in hashtag services . As of March 18 , 2018 , the Ministry of Religious Affairs and Endowments announced that it would be able to pay Hajj pilgrimage to Algiers for the 2018 season .